# Control System Modelling & PID Design (MATLAB/Simulink)

**Tools:MATLAB, Simulink/Simscape, Control System Toolbox  
**What I did:System identification, transfer function modelling, PID tuning, response analysis.

## Highlights
- Identified system parameters from experimental data
- Simulated proportional and PID controllers
- Compared simulation vs experimental response (overshoot, rise time, settling time, SSE)

## Files in this folder
- report-summary.pdf 
- plots/ (response plots)
- matlab-scripts/ (scripts used)
- simulink/ (screenshots or models)
